title: Treasury Wines Shares Jump 8% After Distributor Settlement
description: Australian vintner Treasury Wines Estates Ltd. has reached a settlement with a major US distributor that had decided to stop operating in the lucrative California market, pushing its shares up by the most in 16 months.
